# Sales Analysis with Excel 📊

This project analyzes a dataset of sales transactions using Microsoft Excel.  
It demonstrates practical skills in *data analysis, pivot tables, and data visualization*.

## 📂 Project Files
- Sales_Analysis_Project.xlsx: Contains the raw data, pivot tables, and charts.

## 🔍 Key Insights
- Identified top-performing categories (Electronics, Clothing, Stationery).
- Created pivot tables to summarize sales by product and category.
- Visualized sales trends using bar and column charts.

## 🛠 Tools & Skills
- Microsoft Excel  
- Data Cleaning  
- Pivot Tables  
- Charts & Visualization  

